CheapUnhappyAndalusianhorse-size_restricted.gif&h=74b59d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n次回合繼續演技大爆發 推鳩人 再吹走人個入波<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/8-15-2020/tU80mV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F8-15-2020%2FtU80mV.gif&h=2a4ce383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑鳩阿狗<br />\n2011越位入波 兩黃一紅 紅鳩曼聯名宿 再連入兩球出線<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/AuO8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2FAuO8.gif&h=72bcf729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑鳩鈀狗 仲要J到史上最強反勝<br />\n哨牙蘇插水 掂頸變頭痛 <br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/PepperyAdvancedGopher-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FPepperyAdvancedGopher-max-1mb.gif&h=2668a8bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑鳩車狗<br />\n唔撚使講啦<br />\n疤迷講到兩回合計直頭係巴塞畀車狗黑反轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/3-16-2016/oWjnm_.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F3-16-2016%2FoWjnm_.gif&h=df3efa81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d55e617d1b2de6472bb3daddb128f0ab245a29dd","tid":2157850,"uid":5482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808f61ff6c5608589f248bdf8e122d9a938e3aa4","tid":2157850,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:20:50.000Z","msg":"巴菜 同 亞軍庭有大賽應該收起美欺 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能會贏"},{"pid":"a492ed4245c57f340eda853c78b7c85bff31d296","tid":2157850,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c8287886e54252a36208515bb4621c34707407","tid":2157850,"uid":35293,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-